{"tid":1009772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[贏] 默克爾：華為要保證不交數據予中國　方能參與德國 5G 建設","createTime":"2019-02-05T12:15:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-05T16:56:48.000Z","uid":141151,"like":3,"dislike":80,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"5749b82203809a6f9537da4376a86e73ca00fa99","tid":1009772,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T12:15:22.000Z","msg":"默克爾：華為要保證不交數據予中國　方能參與德國 5G 建設<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/international/%E9%BB%98%E5%85%8B%E7%88%BE-%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E8%A6%81%E4%BF%9D%E8%AD%89%E4%B8%8D%E4%BA%A4%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A%E4%BA%88%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E6%96%B9%E8%83%BD%E5%8F%83%E8%88%87%E5%BE%B7%E5%9C%8B-5g-%E5%BB%BA%E8%A8%AD/?fbclid=IwAR21sbY_9FcV4U-W_iK1T-aqVQ79Ng32WpyV0oeFTIpyI0Dxv6tdRiVRLC8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E9%25BB%2598%25E5%2585%258B%25E7%2588%25BE-%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2582%25BA%25E8%25A6%2581%25E4%25BF%259D%25E8%25AD%2589%25E4%25B8%258D%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E6%2595%25B8%25E6%2593%259A%25E4%25BA%2588%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B-%25E6%2596%25B9%25E8%2583%25BD%25E5%258F%2583%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E5%259C%258B-5g-%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%25A8%25AD%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR21sbY_9FcV4U-W_iK1T-aqVQ79Ng32WpyV0oeFTIpyI0Dxv6tdRiVRLC8&d=Hj%2FeMeEVpmzVIwD%2FtvFBFiHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=cf1eaa66\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E9%25BB%2598%25E5%2585%258B%25E7%2588%25BE-%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2582%25BA%25E8%25A6%2581%25E4%25BF%259D%25E8%25AD%2589%25E4%25B8%258D%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E6%2595%25B8%25E6%2593%259A%25E4%25BA%2588%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B-%25E6%2596%25B9%25E8%2583%25BD%25E5%258F%2583%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E5%259C%258B-5g-%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%25A8%25AD%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR21sbY_9FcV4U-W_iK1T-aqVQ79Ng32WpyV0oeFTIpyI0Dxv6tdRiVRLC8&h=a97debd6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/international/%E9%BB%98%E5%85%8B%E7%88%BE-%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E8%A6%81%E4%BF%9D%E8%AD%89%E4%B8%8D%E4%BA%A4%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A%E4%BA%88%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E6%96%B9%E8%83%BD%E5%8F%83%E8%88%87%E5%BE%B7%E5%9C%8B-5g-%E5%BB%BA%E8%A8%AD/?fbclid=IwAR21sbY_9FcV4U-W_iK1T-aqVQ79Ng32WpyV0oeFTIpyI0Dxv6tdRiVRLC8</a><br />\n<br />\n近期多國政府都關注中國電訊商華為 5G 設備對國家安全構成潛在風險。德國總理默克爾今日表明，華為要保證不會將數據交予中國政府，方可以參與德國的5G 網絡建設。<br />\n<br />\n正於日本訪問的默克爾在一場大學演講上表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">由於安全方面的考慮，有必要與中國政府溝通，確保華為不會將數據交給政府。她又表明如果中國企業想在德國發展，必須保證中國政府無法取得產品中的數據。<br />\n</span><br />\n近期多國政府都關注華為 5G 設備構成風險，可能會被中國情報機關用作竊取機密之用，擬抵制其產品及通訊設備。美國、澳洲、日本等多個國家，近期都宣佈禁止或考慮禁止使用華為設備。不過德國政府一直尚未表態是否跟隨其他國家，將華為排除在市場之外。<br />\n<br />\nMerkel sets out condition for Huawei&lsquo;s participation in 5G network<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/us-huwawei-europe-germany-merkel/merkel-sets-out-condition-for-huaweis-participation-in-5g-network-idUSKCN1PU0GZ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-huwawei-europe-germany-merkel%2Fmerkel-sets-out-condition-for-huaweis-participation-in-5g-network-idUSKCN1PU0GZ&d=Hj%2FeMeEVpmzVIwD%2FtvFBFiHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=2b0f6225\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-huwawei-europe-germany-merkel%2Fmerkel-sets-out-condition-for-huaweis-participation-in-5g-network-idUSKCN1PU0GZ&h=67af1ef4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reuters.com/article/us-huwawei-europe-germany-merkel/merkel-sets-out-condition-for-huaweis-participation-in-5g-network-idUSKCN1PU0GZ</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets